tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE ShippingCosts (
  shipment_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  weight DECIMAL,
  distance DECIMAL,
  shipping_method VARCHAR(50),
  cost DECIMAL
);

CREATE TABLE shipping_costs (
    id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    destination TEXT,
    weight DECIMAL,
    distance DECIMAL,
    shipping_method TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE shipping_history ( 
    id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY, 
    item_id INT, 
    shipping_date DATE, 
    shipping_cost DECIMAL(10,2), 
    FOREIGN KEY (item_id) REFERENCES shipping_costs(id) 
);

CREATE TABLE ShippingHistory (
    id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    shipping_date DATE,
    package_id INTEGER,
    cost DECIMAL,
    location_id INTEGER,
    FOREIGN KEY (package_id) REFERENCES ShippingCosts(id),
    FOREIGN KEY (location_id) REFERENCES ShippingLocations(id)
);

CREATE TABLE shipping_costs (
    id SERIAL,
    item_name TEXT,
    weight DECIMAL,
    destination TEXT,
    shipping_method TEXT,
    cost DECIMAL
);

CREATE TABLE customers (
    id SERIAL,
    customer_name TEXT,
    address TEXT,
    city TEXT,
    state TEXT,
    zip_code TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE orders (
    id SERIAL,
    order_date DATE,
    customer_id INT,
    item_id INT,
    quantity INT
);
